## 7. HOTEL ISOLATION

ALL queries use strict .eq('hotel_id', id). No OR-null ever.
Every insert saves hotel_id. QR URL embeds hotel UUID.
NEVER use .or('hotel_id.eq.X,hotel_id.is.null') — causes cross-contamination.

