## 10. RESTAURANT / RESERVATION SYSTEM

- No auto-print when GUEST submits booking (removed — auto-print was bad UX)
- Walk-in booking: manual 🖨 Print button in success card (reservation agent clicks if needed)
- Booking validation: checks closed_days + opening/closing_time before insert
- Duplicate check: same guest cannot book same restaurant same date while Pending
- Rejection: professional "Dear [Guest Name]..." message saved to rejection_reason
- Guest notification: realtime on restaurant_bookings UPDATE → popup with rejection_reason

RESERVATION AGENT:
- Occupation: Reservation Agent → F&B dept
- fetchTasks adds .neq('service_key','room_service') → sees ONLY restaurant requests
- Auto-redirects to restaurant portal on login

