## 11. CONCIERGE SYSTEM

Flow A (SLA): Luggage → requests table → staff accept/complete
Flow B (Booking): Tours/Taxi/Car Rental → concierge_bookings table
  - Staff confirm/cancel from active tab (Concierge Bookings section in StaffPortal)
  - Cancel requires mandatory reason → "Dear Valued Guest..." saved to rejection_reason
  - Guest gets instant realtime popup on confirm/cancel

